{"type": "article", "id": 2276, "title": "最方便的海报框架", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-10T01:16:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222328LeOZQSzRpEvHsJVq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t喜欢收藏海报的人不少，但如何保存或者张贴海报呢？美国设计师 Brandon Knowlden 带来一款简易的海报框架 STiiCKs ，只需要将上访的木条固定于墙上夹住海报的上部边缘，再将另一条木条夹住海报的底部自然垂坠就可以了。STiiCKs 可以帮助用户省下一笔裱框费用，也方便于更换海报，调节室内气氛。定价 30 美元，<a href=\"http://www.ckie.com/products/stiicks-magnetic-poster-frame#.VA8pX2SSw0A\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222324XiybApm9UaWMB3fI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222325RseC3okzB75G2qhj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.603125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222325uUrjmgCJoZspciwY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.603125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222327E3DqWSoK6MRgxZz0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}